ained for that.\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brauman\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2098}, {\"ngram\": \"Lyles\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2109}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2159}, {\"ngram\": \"the rounds\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2180}, {\"ngram\": \"any aspiring double-r.\\u00c2\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the world championships in 2022, Lyles clocked a 19.31-seconds 200-meter dash, only 0.12 off Bolt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s world mark.\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2357, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world championships\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2267}, {\"ngram\": \"Lyles\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2282}, {\"ngram\": \"a 19.31-seconds 200-meter dash\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2321}, {\"ngram\": \"Bolt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s world mark\", \"from\": 2337, \"to\": 2356}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Right around then, his dream of doubling rounded into view.\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Right around then, his dream\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2386}, {\"ngram\": \"view\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009923 world championships, Netflix film crew in tow, he decided to attempt the double and see how it went.\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2531, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009923 world championships\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2450}, {\"ngram\": \"tow\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pretty well, it turns out; he won both.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThat put him in a totally different conversation,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says Lyles\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 mother, Keisha Bishop.\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2652, \"end\": 2658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keisha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.